item.title: ZW32-12F-High-Voltage-Intelligent-Vacuum-Circuit-Breaker
item.description: ZW32F-12F outdoor high-voltage AC intelligent vacuum circuit breaker is a user boundary switch independently developed by our company. It is mainly composed of ZW32-12 type outdoor vacuum circuit breaker body, FDR fault detection controller and external voltage transformer. The three parts are electrically connected through aviation sockets and outdoor sealed control cables.
